#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_partitioned_array.py:7
msgid "VTKPartitionedArray — numpy-compatible wrapper for composite datasets."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_partitioned_array.py:9
msgid ""
"This module provides the VTKPartitionedArray class that manages a set of "
"arrays of the same name contained within a composite dataset.  Its main "
"purpose is to provide a Numpy-type interface to composite data arrays which "
"are naturally nothing but a collection of vtkDataArrays."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_partitioned_array.py:14
msgid ""
"It also registers __array_function__ overrides so that standard numpy calls "
"(``numpy.sum``, ``numpy.max``, etc.) are dispatched correctly when handed a "
"VTKPartitionedArray."
msgstr ""

