#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/vtk_partitioned_array.py:265
msgid ""
"Construct a composite array given a container of arrays, a dataset, name and "
"association. It is sufficient to define a container of arrays to define a "
"composite array. It is also possible to initialize an array by defining the "
"dataset, name and array association. In that case, the underlying arrays "
"will be created lazily when they are needed. It is recommended to use the "
"latter method when initializing from an existing composite dataset."
msgstr ""

