"1.],        [ 1.,  1.,  1.],        [ 1.,  1.,  1.]]) algs.mag(v) "
"VTKArray([ 1.73205081,  1.73205081,  1.73205081,  1.73205081,  1.73205081]) "
"v / algs.mag(v) Traceback (most recent call last):   File \"<stdin>\", line "
"1, in <module> ValueError: operands could not be broadcast together with "
"shapes (5,3) (5)"
